OL,7,FFunding to boost PSNI recruitment
OL,8,Fnumbers will be prioritised in future
OL,9,Fmonitoring rounds this year, Finance
OL,10,FMinister John O'Dowd has said.
OL,12,FMr O'Dowd also said that the
OL,13,FDepartment of Justice is to receive #5
OL,14,Fmillion to cover unforeseen costs for
OL,15,Fthe police from dealing with recent
OL,16,Frioting.
